---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import "@/styles/global.css";
---

<Layout>
	<section class="flex min-h-full flex-col items-center justify-center px-6 py-16 text-center">
		<div class="max-w-lg space-y-6 rounded-2xl border border-cip-gray-light bg-white/80 p-10 shadow-lg shadow-cip-gray/10">
			<div>
				<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-cip-gray">Panel temporal</p>
				<h1 class="mt-4 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-cip-black">Bienvenido al portal de eventos</h1>
			</div>
			<p class="text-base text-cip-gray">
				Este panel es provisional mientras se conectan las pantallas definitivas. Ya puedes usar tu sesión para navegar el
				sitio o regresar al inicio.
			</p>
			<div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4">
				<a
					href="/"
					class="rounded-md bg-cip-red px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-cip-red-dark focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-cip-red-dark"
				>
					Ir al inicio
				</a>
				<button
					type="button"
					class="rounded-md border border-cip-gray-light px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-cip-black hover:bg-cip-gray-light/30 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-cip-gray-light"
					onclick="localStorage.removeItem('cipAccessToken'); localStorage.removeItem('cipRefreshToken'); window.location.href = '/login';"
				>
					Cerrar sesión
				</button>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<script type="module" src="/src/scripts/ensure-auth.ts" data-ensure-auth data-redirect-path="/login"></script>
</Layout>
